name: Stay Save
description:
It’s not in my capacity to judge or to take sides between the conflict of two countries as the causes of what’s happening is mainly an escalation of political shie*z. Obviously not a black and white thing. One thing for sure whenever war occurs is that the people will always be the victim and the unfortunate ones. To all the people, families, fathers, mothers, brothers, sisters, children that are in dark and unimaginable hard times, i stand with you.
100 percent of the primary sales profit will be sent to a donation contract for our friends in #Ukraine
